title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1987-09-15
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > TLH > FLAC 2448 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 09/2011
description:
Set 1

Hey Pocky Way, Minglewood Blues, When Push Comes To Shove, Beer Barrel Polka, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Row Jimmy, Queen Jane Approximately, Tennessee Jed, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Black Peter, Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

reviews.review_text: - Best AUD recording of this great show to date.

Great sound! I've been going through the MSG '87 run starting with this show, and this AUD sounds great, totally immersive, and like you're actually there! Phil gets a tad lost in the mix occasionally, but it can't all be perfect. Thanks for taping, Ted, and thanks for the transfer Andrew!
